          selected to dance the pas de deux from Don Quixote. She has performed
          lead roles in numerous ballet classics, including the Lilac Fairy from
          Sleeping Beauty, the Black Swan from Swan Lake, the Snow Queen, Dew
          Drop Fairy, and Clara from The Nutcracker, as well as the Grande Rose
